e: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 1986 Grade: Thiqah (reliable) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24282,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/01\/22\/patience-first-strike-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":8248,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sabr: Reward for patience at first strike is Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty says: O son of Adam, if you are patient and restrained at the first shock of calamity, I would not be pleased with any reward for you less than Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 1597 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32023,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/14\/jihad-al-nafs\/","url_meta":{"origin":8248,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Nafs: Only the strong can defeat their lower-self","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 14, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe strong are not those who defeat people. Rather, the strong are those who defeat their own ego.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 717 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650